movie_title: Star Wars: Episode VII - The Force Awakens
title: Nothing in this film for me
review: The plot is a remake with worse actors, actresses and direction. The idealism is gone. The plot holes are obvious. There aren't any pretty girls that show skin. I am not really sure why this film would have any fans. Maybe gender switch completists???
